1. *Porazgovaraćemo* o planovima za vikend. (We will talk about the plans for the weekend.)
2. Mogli bismo *porazgovarati* o tome šta bismo mogli učiniti. (We could talk about what we could do.)
3. Nisam baš spreman da *porazgovaram* o tome sada. (I'm not quite ready to talk about it now.)
4. Ako želite, možemo *porazgovarati* o tome kasnije. (If you want, we can talk about it later.)
5. Molim vas da *porazgovarate* sa svojim kolegama o tome. (Please talk to your colleagues about it.)
6. Jako je važno da *porazgovaramo* o ovome. (It's really important that we talk about this.)
7. Želim da *porazgovaram* sa vama o nečemu važnom. (I want to talk to you about something important.)
8. Znam da nije lako, ali moramo *porazgovarati* o tome. (I know it's not easy, but we have to talk about it.)
9. Ovaj put ćemo *porazgovarati* o tome kako poboljšati situaciju. (This time we will talk about how to improve the situation.)
10. Nakon što *porazgovaramo*, možemo doneti odluku. (After we talk, we can make a decision.)